Und die Visualisierung des Modells `m10.3`, s. @fig-m103.



::: {.cell fig.asp='0.62' hash='metrische-AV_cache/html/fig-m103_3444165fe75c130287d6c07df538d218'}

```{.r .cell-code}
kidiq2 <-
  kidiq %>% 
  mutate(mom_hs = as.factor(mom_hs))

m10.3a <- 
  stan_glm(
    kid_score ~ mom_iq + mom_hs, 
